## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent studies and articles on the topic. Some sources did not provide specific publication dates, which may affect the currency of the information. Additionally, the complexity of individual responses to music means that findings may not be universally applicable. Further research could explore the long-term effects of music on mood and behavior across different demographics.

